FinMark Dashboard
Welcome to the FinMark Dashboard! This is a modern, dark-themed web app built with Node.js and Express. It features user login, a clean dashboard, demo data, and export optionsâ€”perfect for showcasing a professional dashboard experience.

Getting Started

Prerequisites
Node.js (v14 or newer)
npm

Setup Steps
Clone this repository: 
git clone https://github.com/JyanE26/FinmarkWeb_SD6.git
cd FinmarkWeb_SD6

Install the dependencies: npm install

Start the server: node server.js

Or, if you want auto-reload during development: npx nodemon server.js

Open the app: Go to http://localhost:3000 in your browser.

How to Use
Login: Use any credentials from the users.json file.

Dashboard: Explore your stats, recent activity, uploads, reports, and notifications.

Demo Data: Use the demo/reset buttons to quickly fill the dashboard with sample data or clear it out.

Export: Download logs, uploads, or reports as CSV files with a single click.

Customization
Want to add users? Just edit the users.json file.
Want to tweak the look? Check out the style.css file.
